  "further_info": "Recommended Reading This C1.1 level course will use a student textbook, Headway Advanced (C1) 5th Edition Part A (Oxford University Press) which is the focal point for grammar and vocabulary instruction. It will cover topics ranging from humanity to culture to war. Materials from other sources will be used at the discretion of the Instructor. The general methodological principles adopted for this course are learner-centered and based on integrating all four skills (reading, writing, speaking, and listening).",
